snippet.title: Mega64: "Doug Huggem" Recording Session
snippet.description:
Check out our original "Doug Huggem" video at Gametrailers: http://www.gametrailers.com/video/doug-huggem-mega64/710389

Jon St. John (AKA the voice of Duke Nukem) has decided to join the cast of new game "Doug Huggem," a much more family friendly, appropriate, NICE title. We think he made the right choice.

http://mega64.com
